summary:
Sorry, you have been blocked - This website is using a security service to protect itself from online attacks.

 Why have I been blocked? - There are several actions that could trigger this block including submitting a certain word or phrase, a SQL command or malformed data.

 What can I do to resolve this? - You can email the site owner to let them know you were blocked. Please include what you were doing when this page came up and the Cloudflare Ray ID found at the bottom of this page.
proposal:
Hello there, fantastic community! 👋

We understand that just like a SQL command protecting a website from online attacks, your project is looking to secure its position in the crypto market. We're here to offer you some B2B tools that can help you fortify your defenses and expand your territory, just like a well-structured database. 

From creating your own DEX based on Uniswap V2 to launching an IDO pool, we've got a range of tools that can be customized to your project's needs. Our tools are like the Cloudflare Ray ID at the bottom of the page - they're here to support and protect your project's growth. 

And just like resolving a block, we're always available to discuss how these tools can be tailored to your project. So, if you're interested, let's connect and discuss how we can help you build your project's future. 

P.S. Don't worry, we promise not to block you! 😄

Check out our demos here: https://t.me/onoutdemos
